- Inputs include schema model repos, ingest spec repo, business use cases, Confluence links, credentials, and branch metadata.
- Runtime services include VS Code LM API, deterministic extractors, LLM sub-agents, and MCP tools.
- Integrations include GitLab, Confluence, and Lakehouse/Legend.
- Outputs include normalized ER design, MatViews, Summary MatViews, review-ready PURE artifacts, and merge request delivery.
